      <p id="tribute-info"> <b><pre>"Ilan Ramon was an Israeli fighter pilot and later the first Israeli astronaut.
 Ramon was a Space Shuttle payload specialist of STS-107, the fatal mission of Columbia,
 in which he and six other crew members were killed in the re-entry accident.
        At 48, he was the oldest member of the crew."</pre></b></p>
